l de întoarcere sau de circuit;\n\nd) pentru călătoriile întreprinse în scopuri politice, ştiinţifice, culturale,  sportive:\n- invitaţii, bilete de intrare, programe în care să fie înscris,  acolo unde este posibil, numele organizaţiei-gazdă şi durata vizitei\n\nMai multe detalii sunt stabilite în:\n- art.26 al Legii 28/2024: https://www.legis.md/cautare/getResults?doc_id=142194&lang=ro','ro','2025-04-08 23:45:45.432502','2025-04-08 23:45:45.432502','[0.15088656544685364, 0.14604932069778442, -0.3883475363254547, -0.2673777639865875, 0.2687000334262848, 0.07009312510490417, 0.0007016430026851594, -0.023983396589756012, -0.13128012418746948, 0.22515971958637238, 0.10997964441776276, -0.03806688264012337, 0.19927242398262024, -0.06253299862146378, 0.07675572484731674, 0.10157337784767151, -0.3594711422920227, -0.08639754354953766, -0.07031480967998505, 0.10082373023033142, 0.09482361376285553, -0.20621086657047272, 0.06329032778739929, 0.023785315454006195, 0.05091096833348274, 0.21936066448688507, -0.027120405808091164, -0.1568777859210968, 0.051805950701236725, -0.10284972190856934, -0.11059711128473282, 0.18769808113574982, -0.18793299794197083, 0.2616199851036072, -0.08362369984388351, 0.18335719406604767, 0.1131678968667984, -0.06102679669857025, 0.3273877203464508, 0.010596785694360733, 0.11216162890195847, -0.2154426872730255, 0.2902916371822357, 0.25022199749946594, -0.11770042032003403, -0.16763463616371155, 0.18824435770511627, 0.18201817572116852, -0.23252767324447632, 0.015231123194098473, -0.049527041614055634, -0.09760819375514984, -0.1227327287197113, 0.1547320932149887, 0.03273438662290573, 0.005794995464384556, 0.15020079910755157, 0.020883655175566673, -0.10821808129549026, -0.054072149097919464, 0.005053533241152763, 0.024559421464800835, -0.31459707021713257, 0.09446971118450165, -0.17093972861766815, 0.03527216985821724, -0.0738983154296875, 0.24409161508083344, -0.13699783384799957, 0.04603735730051994, -0.2451290637254715, -0.11504288017749786,